Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.63,0:00:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心就能神奇地变得坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背后仿佛有你的脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追赶了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我频频回头看着你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新恋情的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是两人在不知不觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:01:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展开看不见的爱情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以永远不愿分离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓我只爱你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我又毁灭了一个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要，我不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.25,0:02:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明杀了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.99,0:02:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我好不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易跟我喜欢的人告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还想跟我喜欢的人\N一起做好多好多的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经不会死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管用世界上的任何武器\N恐怕都无法…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，没有人能杀得了你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也没有人能阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有个老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很怕寂寞\N常常让我很头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说，她是个很难侍侯\N很麻烦的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管如此，我还是很爱她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我会死在这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许已经不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说，我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想见我心爱的女人\N把她拥在怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能活着，真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有心爱的男人，真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打酸把它记住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住那些被我毁掉的\N城镇的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定曾经有很多人\N在那里生活过的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打酸努力把它记住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概没有人能够原谅\N我所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望老天爷至少\N允许我拥有这两个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#05谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动词的五段活用有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否定形，连用形，终止形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连体形，假设形，命令形…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么白日梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太扯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你个头啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地…地震…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是赶快…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快去避难比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说等警报铃声乡了\N才开始避难演习的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么讨厌我的课吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，我尿急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎么了，修…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，慢一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.56,0:06:44.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑太快了啦，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是轰炸吗？还是飞弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，什么来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你，你先逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是男女朋友耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃当然一起逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，危险的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，来的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个很大的地震
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且性能还不完整
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一把这么大的地震\N误当作是被攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我会做出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点逃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，不要看我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是她的男朋友啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来只受损了这点程度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要毁掉这所学校\N也是轻而易举
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是看到了\N什么很可怕的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？地震呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，对不起，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修，怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是因为刚才那件事\N使我的身体某处故障了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.97,0:10:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对于千濑的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说，刚才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.27,0:10:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我错误启动了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很迟钝\N总是会做出危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我现在已经\N稍微能控制力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才也只稍微爆炸一下\N就控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过相对的，我好像故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.53,0:11:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.63,0:11:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是跟你说了\N不要跟我道歉吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧，千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟他们一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去，我会死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是武器，所以需要维修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像人类需要吃药一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好整修一下\N我会没命的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了，明天学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你不生气呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道是谁害你受这种苦的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是那个老头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是把你的身体\N改造成这样的成员之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你还要听这种人的话？\N那个…可以走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你不会不甘心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，我还有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天晚上到展望台来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会等你来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啦，明美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑和修次还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.02,0:12:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次他…修次他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个班级点名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，原来你平安无事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她受了一点伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直升机送她去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊，那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你们这种自私的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出事的时候\N只会给大家带来麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那是什么眼神？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙\N也是靠千濑在保护着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部到齐了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉，我不是存心要打你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是一时冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我，明美，大家都很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，我打酸休学去加入军队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:24.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保护一个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论这个世界发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想保护这个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我一直以来的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保护明美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧，修次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴，你跟我表白有什么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的好羡慕小淳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的四周\N好多人事物都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修次，你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有受伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（紧急出动）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良平，辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在死之前\N没有感到痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你好像是青森人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里离千濑的地域蛮近的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还很和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片你带着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿铁小队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑妹妹…今天没来\N是不是去约会了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.26,0:16:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知道就不要跟她分手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在还是很喜欢她的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊，中村
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如让千濑杀死酸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以把一切\N都推给那孩子承受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还只是个高中生女孩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们要死得这么痛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被千濑杀死时\N一点痛苦都没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样好像有点赖皮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为今后这个星球会更…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.76,0:17:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被千濑的口头禅傅染了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.81,0:18:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起喔，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要等我喔，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一次我一定会赴约的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告中队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在关东一带的战况是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要这样乱来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.15,0:18:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经透过卫星得知战况了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没有按照我的指示行动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是无可奈何的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么，大家都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是无可奈何的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立刻出动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照这样下去\N战况会越来越惨烈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在展望台等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得快点去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的朋友现在不在展望台
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据监视部队傅来的消息…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非去不可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修一定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个城市会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不准对我开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一眨眼的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我回神过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是孤伶伶一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是，我军部队…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去的话，一定会死更多人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是死的不是我认识的\N不是我喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.26,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取而代之的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些注定要\N被我杀的人死掉罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说，有什么不同呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.27,0:20:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是一样的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了只会让我更难过痛苦以外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你们让我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他…我的男朋友在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少，今天一天就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想在这个城市杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么阿修没有来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？是情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修的监视记录？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.82,0:21:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想听！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想看这种事！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬美学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点来啊，阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说\N你有很多话要跟我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有很多很多话想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不谈恋爱了\N我不知道会变成什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有味道耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就这样，一直待到天亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后，千濑慢慢的开口说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:43.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中有一道裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以入眠的夜里总不停的叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉黎明已悄然到来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么想听见你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.35,0:23:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感受你的体温
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.52,0:23:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你的思念越来越强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泪水夺眶而出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了我心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍无法忘怀你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然只因一句再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.29,0:23:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫人感到悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.53,0:24:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是千濑的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.54,0:24:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这么喜欢她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.04,0:24:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千濑，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.34,0:24:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终兵器彼女下一回\N[同学]
